{"tid":1276844,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"玩家傻眼！《爐石戰記》全球竟隨陸版和諧卡牌美術圖","createTime":"2019-07-02T05:07:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T09:28:47.000Z","uid":2765,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"e9605081949bda7020ada733db6626de7077c882","tid":1276844,"uid":2765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T05:07:40.000Z","msg":"暴雪旗下卡牌遊戲《爐石戰記》的最新資料片《奧丹姆守護者》將於下個月上市，今（7/2）日進行預先改版，不過沒想到改版後被玩家發現，許多原些卡牌的美術圖都因為不等的裸露與暴力元素慘遭「和諧」，引發國內外玩家一片罵聲。<br />\n<br />\n據玩家統計，這次被和諧的卡牌共有8張，包含了「保密者」、「風怒鷹身人」、「致命射擊」、「碎顱」、「撕咬」、「剔骨」、「苦痛仕女」、「魅魔」，特別是魅魔還直接被移除，換成了功能相同的「惡魔潛獵者」，讓不少玩家傻眼。而由於在先前陸版就已經公開了其中5張修正後的圖，眾所周知對岸對於遊戲中色情、暴力的元素一項不友善，過去在《魔獸世界》陸版就有許多怪物因此被修改，但沒想到這次《爐石戰記》的修改不僅僅是陸版還闊及全球。讓許多玩家不禁嘲諷「這是兒童版嗎？」"},{"pid":"8cf8f6f8b121f372beeba217a3508d5379c71925","tid":1276844,"uid":2765,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T05:08:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://game.ettoday.net/amp/amp_news.php?news_id=1479871&amp;fbclid=IwAR3y3cncnUVa904zz-vyySS888rLKo8l-Ja-0Pqox6eAMdM1d-jx0juEo6g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgame.ettoday.net%2Famp%2Famp_news.php%3Fnews_id%3D1479871%26fbclid%3DIwAR3y3cncnUVa904zz-vyySS888rLKo8l-Ja-0Pqox6eAMdM1d-jx0juEo6g&d=nd52c%2FRhS%2BUv0SpwCnLJ%2Bh0Z1crOiE0eyIPSb4MeDzY%3D&h=9a083857\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://game.ettoday.net/amp/amp_news.php?news_id=1479871&amp;fbclid=IwAR3y3cncnUVa904zz-vyySS888rLKo8l-Ja-0Pqox6eAMdM1d-jx0juEo6g</a>                                                                                                 <br />\n<br />\n以後唔會再玩垃圾爐石<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7bcf636f61f5b313d42eb7d24fb8e125c60282b","tid":1276844,"uid":2765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T05:15:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9b5344473e33abca36ddaa8c36a80abe8ee7f1a6","tid":1276844,"u